@startuml
title Autonumber Examples

participant A
participant B
participant C

autonumber
A -> B : First message
B -> C : Second message
C --> B : Third message
B --> A : Fourth message

autonumber 10
A -> B : Starts at 10
B -> C : Number 11

autonumber 20 10
A -> B : Starts at 20
B -> C : Increment by 10 (30)
C -> A : Next is 40

autonumber stop
A -> B : No number
B -> C : Still no number

autonumber resume
C -> A : Resumes numbering

autonumber "<b>[000]"
A -> B : Formatted 001
B -> C : Formatted 002

@enduml
